<p>The mum-of-two, 40, followed a recipe by Donna Hay and said she usually cooks lamb cutlets when entertaining guests or to celebrate special moments, as this type of meat cut is quite expensive.</p>

<p>'Lamb cutlets are a little bit pricey at times, so I look out for when they're on special,' Jules posted on Instagram.</p>

